Text: Hellosdid it I finally took a minute to email you How are you Mom and Dad just moved to Arkanshire Retirement Village this week Went over to help and pick up a load of stuff It has been tuff to deal with but know it is a good idea for them Jason is here for a visit broken hip and all so between two jobs and all this I am a little fritzed at the momment Heard you and I both have a Jeff in our lives We will have to talk Maybe we can begin communicating a little better Love you mb
